  %p
    The US Go Congress is the largest Go event in the United States. It
    happens once a year and spans one week. Events include the US Open, the
    largest annual Go tournament in the US, professional lectures and game
    analysis, continuous self paired games, and all kinds of Go related
    activities from morning to midnight. Come for the Go, come for the
    comradery of old friends, come for the relaxing mountain air. Whatever
    your reason, we are looking forward to seeing you there.
  %p
    Attending the US Go Congress or any of the AGA sponsored events at the Blue
    Ridge Assembly is as easy as:
    %ul
      %li
        = link_to "Start Here", new_user_registration_path
        to create an account
      %li
        = link_to "Sign In", new_user_session_path
        to manage your account
      %li Check back regularly for updates


  %div{:style => "clear:left;"}

- @contents.each do |c|
  %h3= c.subject
  = Markdown.new(c.body).to_html.html_safe

